Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.75,0:00:29.04,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,果然不是对手呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.62,0:00:30.33,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.75,0:00:32.37,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,我不是已经解释过了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.50,0:00:34.16,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,你去问老君就知道了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.25,0:00:35.75,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,我会信么？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.87,0:00:36.83,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,搞定了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.25,0:00:37.91,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,搞〜定〜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.54,0:00:42.29,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,那是在你追随老君之前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.79,0:00:44.95,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,不信的话我可以陪你去见老君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.12,0:00:45.75,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,荒谬
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.00,0:00:48.29,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,老君是你想见就能见的么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.29,0:00:48.37,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,老君是你想见就能见的么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.25,0:00:53.83,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,灵体…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.54,0:00:55.87,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.54,0:00:56.87,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.83,0:00:58.79,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,别插手…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.87,0:00:59.66,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,你不是他对手啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.79,0:01:03.00,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,刚才是你的能力么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.29,0:01:04.54,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,难怪你可以盗取天明珠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.04,0:01:05.75,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.00,0:01:07.95,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.16,0:01:09.08,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,小黑…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.79,0:01:10.58,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,你个坏蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.08,0:01:11.62,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,小白
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.95,0:01:12.91,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,你先进去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.00,0:01:13.41,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.54,0:01:14.50,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,没事的，乖~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.75,0:01:15.62,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,带小黑进去~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.33,0:01:18.37,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.50,0:01:19.70,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,大不了摊牌嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.29,0:01:24.20,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,看来你并不打算交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.70,0:01:25.50,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,我说了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.62,0:01:26.91,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,这是老君提出的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.20,0:01:32.62,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,躲？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.00,0:01:34.04,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,寻找战机嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.41,0:01:39.91,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,井啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.25,0:01:42.12,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,我的菜！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.41,0:01:44.41,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,果子！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.25,0:01:59.62,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,好茶！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.79,0:02:01.29,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,爷爷你醒醒啊爷爷！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.12,0:02:02.70,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.37,0:02:04.29,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.37,0:02:05.00,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,你谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.12,0:02:06.45,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,这种时候不要吐槽…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.83,0:02:07.50,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,我们在这边…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.87,0:02:10.04,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,有点奇怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.79,0:02:11.87,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,他在隐藏实力？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.12,0:02:12.83,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,别逞强了，一起上吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.91,0:02:13.54,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,他根本没有认真
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.54,0:02:15.04,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,别急
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.41,0:02:19.29,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,主场来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.04,0:02:20.79,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,你的眼睛还看得到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.12,0:02:22.00,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,小问题
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.70,0:02:24.20,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,我们来打个赌吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.33,0:02:25.25,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,唔？人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.87,0:02:27.00,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,你去那里干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.37,0:02:28.12,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.37,0:02:29.50,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,那你在干什么呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.87,0:02:30.58,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,避雨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.08,0:02:31.79,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,战斗呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.08,0:02:32.66,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,暂停
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.91,0:02:33.66,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.04,0:02:34.95,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,我讨厌下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.12,0:02:37.70,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,怎么能半途而废呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.50,0:02:39.25,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,可以进屋打
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.62,0:02:42.58,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,下雨天的湿了身多不好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.70,0:02:44.66,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,休息休息喝口茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.83,0:02:57.29,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,为什么会变成这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.66,0:03:10.04,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,怎么会下这么大…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.54,0:03:12.20,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,我好担心比丢啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.41,0:03:14.41,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,没事的，那里很安全
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.08,0:03:15.58,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,小冰子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.91,0:03:16.95,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,谁是小冰子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.79,0:03:18.62,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,你怕暴雨么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.25,0:03:21.00,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,不会呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.45,0:03:23.87,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,六里外有房屋倒塌，有人被埋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.87,0:03:24.87,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,在哪个方向！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.20,0:03:26.04,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,正前方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.50,0:03:27.16,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,避雨亭！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.25,0:03:28.20,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,我去救人!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.29,0:03:28.50,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,恩!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.66,0:03:29.70,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,哥哥小心啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.91,0:03:30.29,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,恩！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.79,0:03:34.16,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,你是怎么知道的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.45,0:03:35.12,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,听到的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.83,0:03:36.62,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,你是妖精么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.29,0:03:37.87,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.37,0:03:39.87,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,你貌似也不坏嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.20,0:03:41.37,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,你叫什么名字？
Comment: 0,0:03:42.75,0:03:43.20,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,谛听
Comment: 0,0:03:45.41,0:03:46.04,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,谛听？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.62,0:03:47.79,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,爷爷你知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.35,0:03:50.10,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,谛听可是上古神兽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.12,0:03:50.79,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.91,0:03:52.33,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,那你应该是好人吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.45,0:03:53.91,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,为什么要打哥哥呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.37,0:03:56.04,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,你知道我是妖精不怕么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.25,0:03:58.04,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,不怕呀，哥哥不也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.91,0:03:59.95,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,你居然知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.33,0:04:01.12,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,你不怕他么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.95,0:04:04.54,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,为什么要怕，他可是我哥哥耶！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.33,0:04:06.41,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,那你也知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.12,0:04:21.29,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,斥冰焰！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.70,0:04:22.41,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,是谁！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.58,0:04:24.58,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,没时间想这个了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.25,0:04:32.04,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.29,0:04:33.50,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,不是被冲走了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.79,0:04:34.54,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,玄离
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.95,0:04:41.25,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,斥冰焰是你用来试我的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.79,0:04:42.45,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.70,0:04:43.62,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.75,0:04:45.29,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,人我已经救走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.62,0:04:47.83,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,果然瞒不过你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.12,0:04:49.58,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,你是怎么看出来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.20,0:04:51.79,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,只怪我们太熟了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.58,0:04:54.41,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,你早表明身份不就好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.37,0:04:57.00,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,我这不是在隐居嘛~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.37,0:05:01.87,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.04,0:05:04.95,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,是老君的千里传音器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.08,0:05:05.75,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,哇……
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.95,0:05:07.00,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,这么高端？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.45,0:05:09.25,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,恩，是我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.20,0:05:13.41,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,我知道了……
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.33,0:05:16.45,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,喵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.62,0:05:17.91,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,干喵？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:20.16,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,老君要见你们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.70,0:05:22.12,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,啊？为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.45,0:05:23.70,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,他并没有在找我吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.37,0:05:26.50,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,不，是关于天明珠的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.79,0:05:29.20,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,他终于意识到了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.62,0:05:30.50,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.75,0:05:31.83,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,去了就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.45,0:05:43.00,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,原来是哥哥的朋友呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.29,0:05:45.62,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,是啊，刚才是和我们开玩笑的‘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.91,0:05:47.62,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,好像不是很好笑耶…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.87,0:05:49.87,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,是啊，哥哥你都被打出翔了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.29,0:05:52.33,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,难道你一直在追我么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.41,0:05:53.20,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.50,0:05:54.45,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,知道错了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.20,0:05:56.37,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,我也是受害者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.08,0:05:59.45,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.79,0:06:01.16,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,去见神仙呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.04,0:06:03.16,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,我能去么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.08,0:06:04.54,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,可以呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.70,0:06:05.70,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,咦，可以么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.37,0:06:08.37,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,没关系，老君喜欢热闹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.50,0:06:10.50,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,哈哈，那能带小黑么~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.25,0:06:13.00,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,好啊~ (这倒省的解释了）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.58,0:06:15.29,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,那我们几时出发呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.41,0:06:17.58,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,先活过今晚吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.91,0:06:18.54,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,恩…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.87,0:06:20.00,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,别这么开心…
